ComicInfo.Summary:
FINAL ISSUE!
As the Void's Asylum is filled with brand new horrors that the mysterious Lory has brought to Wonderland, Violet is left to deal with the fallout. Will she embrace her destiny as the Mad Hatter and join the carnage, or will she fight and die as a human? The action-packed, emotional ending to Violet Liddle's story is coming!
